0 -14 Td
(Book Insights API is a FastAPI web service backed by a SQLite database. It imports the) Tj
0 -14 Td
(  Goodreads `books.csv` dataset, exposes CRUD endpoints for book records, supports multi-field) Tj
0 -14 Td
(  search, and provides a hybrid similar-books recommendation endpoint.) Tj
